{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Attempted_Arrest_of_Chewbacca",
  "title": "The Attempted Arrest of Chewbacca",
  "summary": "On the Corporate Sector Authority world of Etti IV, the protocol droid C3PO wanders through Capital City's spaceport and parks in search of hyperlane codes, only to stumble onto a tense gathering that includes the Imperial-aligned Chantinelle, the Horansi cub Kuxli, and the Authority enforcer Piper with her attack dog Duke. When Chewbacca arrives to collect his droid, Piper announces there is a warrant for the Wookiee's arrest and refuses to let the pair leave. As Chewbacca tries to flee, the CSA Vice-Prex Alora appears and uses the Force to choke him to his knees, calmly insisting that CSA law will handle the renegade. A squad of Espo guards swarms the struggling Wookiee while Duke savages the shrieking C3PO, and Alora threatens to destroy the droid and crush Chewbacca unless he submits. The confrontation is cut short when the game crashes, leaving the arrest unresolved.",
